229
00:14:44.420 --> 00:14:46.800
♪ <i>With you</i> ♪

230
00:14:48.050 --> 00:14:50.340
♪ <i>With you</i> ♪

231
00:14:51.600 --> 00:14:56.060
♪ <i>With you</i> ♪

232
00:15:01.230 --> 00:15:02.900
Hmm?

233
00:15:07.590 --> 00:15:11.270
You have done what no other
has before.

234
00:15:11.460 --> 00:15:14.770
Because of you. I feel pain.

235
00:15:14.970 --> 00:15:18.480
