259
00:16:25.660 --> 00:16:27.380
Uh. come over.
It's totally cool. guys.

260
00:16:27.580 --> 00:16:28.840
Me and Kam are tight.

261
00:16:29.040 --> 00:16:31.260
In my millennia of existence.

262
00:16:31.460 --> 00:16:33.810
this is the wisest sage
I've ever known.

263
00:16:34.010 --> 00:16:35.680
The fuck?

264
00:16:35.880 --> 00:16:38.810
