Vox Machina.

266
00:16:42.260 --> 00:16:43.610
And just in time.

267
00:16:43.810 --> 00:16:45.860
He's gonna tell us where
all the other vestiges are.

268
00:16:46.060 --> 00:16:47.940
Not quite. wise one.

269
00:16:48.140 --> 00:16:50.630
You will reveal them yourselves.

270
00:16:51.800 --> 00:16:54.550
With this.

271
00:16:57.260 --> 00:17:00.080
The vestige known as Mythcarver.

272
00:17:00.280 --> 00:17:01.540
Connected to all myths

273
00:17:01.740 --> 00:17:05.920
and legends.
including the other vestiges.

274
00:17:07.330 --> 00:17:11.340
Aw. but. Kammi.
I didn't get you anything.

275
00:17:11.540 --> 00:17:12.780
Whoa.

276
00:17:16.610 --> 00:17:21.190
♪ <i>Mythcarver. show me</i> ♪

277
00:17:21.390 --> 00:17:25.270
♪ <i>Something good</i> ♪

278
00:17:25.470 --> 00:17:26.470
<i>Whoa.</i>

279
00:17:26.560 --> 00:17:29.610
<i>Guys. I'm somewhere else.</i>

280
00:17:29.810 --> 00:17:31.780
<i>There's a weird sky.</i>

281
00:17:31.980 --> 00:17:33.280
<i>pink mountains.</i>

282
00:17:33.480 --> 00:17:37.200
<i>and a crazy forest
with upside down waterfalls.</i>

283
00:17:37.400 --> 00:17:38.750
<i>Reminds me of a drug trip.</i>

284
00:17:38.950 --> 00:17:41.670
<i>That sounds
sort of like the Fey Realm.</i>

285
00:17:41.860 --> 00:17:45.670
<i>I see something
inside this gnarly tree.</i>

286
00:17:45.870 --> 00:17:49.970
<i>Oh. Vex. it's some
badass-looking bow.</i>

287
00:17:50.160 --> 00:17:53.220
Isn't the Fey Realm
on another plane of existence?

288
00:17:53.420 --> 00:17:55.510
That's inconvenient.

289
00:17:55.710 --> 00:17:58.140
A shift spell could
get us there. but...

290
00:17:58.340 --> 00:17:59.980
it might not work.

291
00:18:00.170 --> 00:18:02.730
Kiki. think you could try?

292
00:18:02.930 --> 00:18:04.810
Yeah.

293
00:18:05.010 --> 00:18:06.730
- I could.
- Now I'm in a city.

294
00:18:06.930 --> 00:18:08.650
It looks familiar.

295
00:18:08.850 --> 00:18:10.900
<i>I think it's Westruun.</i>

296
00:18:11.100 --> 00:18:12.780
<i>and it's been invaded.</i>

297
00:18:12.980 --> 00:18:15.410
<i>There's a bunch of dudes
who look like Grog.</i>

298
00:18:15.610 --> 00:18:18.910
<i>One's got a vestige.
big giant gauntlets.</i>

299
00:18:19.110 --> 00:18:20.200
<i>They're glowing.</i>

300
00:18:20.400 --> 00:18:22.750
Uh. it's probably not important.

301
00:18:22.950 --> 00:18:25.750
Okay.
What is going on with you?

302
00:18:27.290 --> 00:18:30.130
What was that?

303
00:18:30.330 --> 00:18:33.800
We're not alone.
I'm afraid you've been followed.

304
00:18:35.840 --> 00:18:37.350
Everyone get down!

305
00:18:51.890 --> 00:18:53.800
Yes.

306
00:18:55.050 --> 00:18:57.740
The woman was right.

307
00:18:57.940 --> 00:19:00.950
You have my thanks. gnome.

308
00:19:01.150 --> 00:19:03.790
for finding me a vestige.

309
00:19:09.520 --> 00:19:10.880
Come on. we got to jump in.

310
00:19:11.080 --> 00:19:13.136
With Kam on our side. we can
actually beat this fucker.

311
00:19:13.160 --> 00:19:14.170
Split up.

312
00:19:14.370 --> 00:19:16.360
Hit him where the Sphinx
has drawn blood.

313
00:19:19.490 --> 00:19:22.970
Aren't you
supposed to be extinct?

314
00:19:23.170 --> 00:19:25.870
Not yet. defiler.

315
00:19:32.630 --> 00:19:34.570
I've got the hang of this now.

316
00:19:34.770 --> 00:19:36.710
Oi! Up here.

317
00:19:38.050 --> 00:19:40.590
Hey! Get off him.

318
00:19:47.070 --> 00:19:48.180
Got you.

319
00:20:06.740 --> 00:20:09.230
Does anyone have eyes on him?

320
00:20:09.430 --> 00:20:11.480
Fly us out of here.

321
00:20:11.680 --> 00:20:13.070
Let's go. Kiki.

322
00:20:21.220 --> 00:20:23.330
Give me that jugular.

323
00:20:27.850 --> 00:20:30.640
<i>More! More!</i>

324
00:20:36.860 --> 00:20:38.940
Enough!

325
00:20:50.790 --> 00:20:52.660
Now my prize.

326
00:21:18.940 --> 00:21:20.690
No!

327
00:21:29.490 --> 00:21:32.100
Oh. shit.

328
00:21:32.300 --> 00:21:34.150
No. no. no. no.

329
00:21:34.350 --> 00:21:35.980
Scanlan.

330
00:21:36.180 --> 00:21:38.290
Kammi. no.

331
00:21:39.960 --> 00:21:41.490
Thank you...

332
00:21:41.690 --> 00:21:42.910
for showing me...

333
00:21:43.110 --> 00:21:46.800
Osysa once more.

334
00:21:54.430 --> 00:21:56.590
The vestige is mine.

335
00:21:56.790 --> 00:22:00.720
Nothing can stop
the Chroma Conclave.

336
00:22:00.920 --> 00:22:04.110
least of all you.

337
00:22:05.860 --> 00:22:07.930
<i>I hunger...</i>

338
00:22:08.130 --> 00:22:09.820
For blood.

339
00:22:15.580 --> 00:22:17.770
Hurry.

340
00:22:17.970 --> 00:22:19.690
Bloody wonderful.

341
00:22:19.890 --> 00:22:22.400
- Anyone see another way out?
- I'll try to make us one.

342
00:22:22.600 --> 00:22:23.780
Grog!

343
00:22:23.980 --> 00:22:26.990
Grog. come on.

344
00:22:27.190 --> 00:22:28.990
Come. meat.

345
00:22:36.640 --> 00:22:38.000
Step it up. Keyleth.

346
00:22:41.900 --> 00:22:43.400
Everyone get close.

347
00:22:47.950 --> 00:22:49.850
But he's...

348
00:23:05.050 --> 00:23:07.280
Grog. we got to go.

349
00:23:07.480 --> 00:23:08.910
Yes.

350
00:23:09.110 --> 00:23:11.140
- Grog!
- More.

351
00:23:12.600 --> 00:23:14.910
What are you doing?
We got to leave.

352
00:23:16.740 --> 00:23:17.980
More.

353
00:23:19.640 --> 00:23:22.550
Grog. stop!

354
00:23:26.440 --> 00:23:27.800
Uh... Wha...

355
00:23:36.660 --> 00:23:38.940
Pike?

356
00:23:39.140 --> 00:23:41.190
No.

357
00:23:41.390 --> 00:23:42.790
Pike?

358
00:23:46.690 --> 00:23:48.590
Come on. big guy.
Move!

359
00:23:51.430 --> 00:23:53.700
- Keyleth. spell!
- I need a little more time.

360
00:23:53.900 --> 00:23:56.760
We don't have it. Cast it now.

361
00:24:22.670 --> 00:24:24.570
What happened to Pike?

362
00:24:24.770 --> 00:24:26.570
- Where is she?
- I...

363
00:24:26.770 --> 00:24:27.860
I don't know.

364
00:24:28.060 --> 00:24:30.530
And where's Grog?

365
00:24:30.730 --> 00:24:32.580
And Scanlan?

366
00:24:32.780 --> 00:24:34.640
Where are we?

367
00:25:28.980 --> 00:25:29.980
Chirp.

